Common.Strapline.Common.Text: Class A Office in Dublin, OH

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: Located in the heart of Dublin, Ohio with close access to the Bridge Park development and Tuttle Crossing, Blazer Tech offers a premier Class A opportunity for all office users. This new build office space provides a versatile open floor plate and an above-market parking ratio. Up to 42,000 square feet of white-box space is available which can be demised for multi-tenant use.

Common.Highlight.Common.Text: Businesses can take advantage of full-building and full-floor options that feature move-in ready suites and highly visible signage opportunities.
Newly remodeled - highlighted by modernized common areas, a fitness center, and an indoor/outdoor coffee bar and lounge.
Employees will be treated to an on-site food truck alley and are catty-corner to the Mall at Tuttle Crossing, the area's premier shopping destination.
Conveniently provides direct access to the Outerbelt/I-270 and Tuttle Crossing Boulevard, which lead to downtown Columbus in under 20 minutes.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: Take advantage of a high-end, full-building opportunity thats artfully designed and encompassed by an abundance of amenities.  The Innovation Campus at Lakehurst consists of four buildings offering up to 110,516 square feet of move-in ready space with highly visible exterior signage available to increase brand awareness.  Three of the edifices provide a chance to occupy an entire building, making them perfect for a new headquarters in a recently renovated property with enviable luxuries.  The market-leading tenant amenities include remodeled and fashionably designed common areas, a state-of-the-art fitness center, a grab and go vending room, and a wi-fi enabled courtyard.  Employees can also take a single step outside and be treated to an assortment of local cuisine in the on-site food truck alley.  The search for off-site shopping and entertainment will be brief as employees find themselves near the Mall at Tuttle Crossing, which serves them their favorite stores, including Victorias Secret, Bath and Body Works, Pottery Barn, and more.  Commuters to Innovation Campus will find its a breeze connecting to Columbus and the surrounding areas given the business parks direct access to Tuttle Crossing Boulevard as well as The Outerbelt/I-270, which lead to downtown Columbus in under 20 minutes.  They can also reach John Glenn International Airport within a 25-minute drive.  The Innovation Campus at Lakehurst provides businesses the perfect opportunity to occupy modernly designed, move-in ready spaces within reach of market-leading amenities.
